es the scatter of UV-based $M_{\\rm BH}$ estimates by $\\sim15\\%$ when\ncompared to previous studies. Lastly, we discuss the potential of our\nprescriptions to provide more accurate and precise estimates of $M_{\\rm BH}$\ngiven a much larger sample of quasars at $3.20 \\lesssim z \\lesssim 3.50$, where\nboth Mg II and H$\\beta$ can be measured in the same near-infrared spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Apr 2023 22:00:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-06"}
