l volume flux of cavity-filling, which is\nentirely contributed by this shrinking, scales as ${Q_T\\simeq 2\\pi R Z_c U_c}$;\nremains a constant throughout the collapse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Apr 2023 14:38:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-06"}
